name: TGE Logistic
author: TGE

sections.description:
The Garuda Express (TGE) is pioneer in courier/messenger/same day/rush and freight delivery anywhere throughout Nepal. We provide excellent on-time service for firms-companies, hospitals, centers, groups, retailers, and labs throughout Nepal.

Our Core Values
– Every Time on Time
– Experts in time-sensitive deliveries
– Door to door delivery
– Available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week
– Same day pick up and same day delivery
– Globally connected, locally invested
– No. 1 Shipping solution for E-Commerce

TGE App offers the following features:

  • Place Order Directly From Woocommerce to TGE panel
sections.faq:
How do I get TGE API for Woocommerce ?

TGE only provides API key to their valid registered merchants. To get your API key please contact us at +977-01-4602416.
